headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Business Battle Bonuses
content: It’s a bull market out there, as far as illicit cargo is concerned. You might notice that Business Battles are occurring more often because of this spike in supply. It’s your job to satisfy the demand — in return, you’ll be rewarded with Double Rewards on all Business Battles, as well as the Orange Skull Emissive Mask and Street Crimes Red Gangs Tee for winning the Event Cargo.
